12:24.952 --> 12:28.497
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>So, um...</i>

12:28.581 --> 12:30.207
<i>who are you?</i>

12:30.291 --> 12:31.834
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Oh, okay.</i>

12:31.917 --> 12:33.335
<i>So we're doing this now?</i>

12:33.419 --> 12:35.045
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>(chuckles) Yeah, why not?</i>

12:35.129 --> 12:36.547
(laughter nearby)

12:36.630 --> 12:38.716
<i>Hey, I'll go first.</i>

12:38.799 --> 12:40.342
<i>I'm Phil.</i>

12:40.426 --> 12:42.178
<i>Phil Hayes.</i>

12:42.261 --> 12:44.722
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Annie, Annie Mitchell.</i>

12:44.805 --> 12:48.642
<i>Whoa, did we just enter</i>
<i>a whole new level of intimacy?</i>

12:48.726 --> 12:51.187
<i>I think so, yeah.</i>
