13:26.514 --> 13:28.891
<i>Phil from Ashford.</i>

13:32.186 --> 13:33.729
<i>You know, there is</i>
<i>something kind of romantic</i>

13:33.812 --> 13:35.523
<i>about all of this, right?</i>

13:35.606 --> 13:37.191
<i>Like, I don't really</i>
<i>know who you are,</i>

13:37.274 --> 13:39.026
<i>you don't really know who I am,</i>

13:39.109 --> 13:42.363
<i>we're hundreds of miles away</i>
<i>from each other, and yet</i>

