<i>Hey, promise me</i>
<i>you won't look me up.</i>

13:50.996 --> 13:52.540
<i>It'll just ruin this whole</i>

13:52.623 --> 13:54.416
You've Got Mail <i> moment</i>
<i>we're having.</i>

13:54.500 --> 13:56.252
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Yeah, okay.</i>

13:56.335 --> 13:58.254
<i>-I promise,</i> Shopgirl.
<i>-(both laugh)</i>

13:58.337 --> 14:00.714
<i>Plus, it's actually</i>
<i>better you don't know</i>

14:00.798 --> 14:02.925
<i>that I'm a 400-pound guy</i>
<i>living in my parents' basement.</i>

14:03.008 --> 14:04.301
<i>(Annie laughs)</i>

14:07.555 --> 14:09.515
(chuckles quietly)

14:13.811 --> 14:15.646
(mumbles quietly)

14:27.366 --> 14:29.827
(sighs)

14:38.210 --> 14:40.129
Oh, wow.

14:40.212 --> 14:42.214
(sighs)

14:51.390 --> 14:53.475
<i>Hey, Annie?</i>

14:53.559 --> 14:55.227
<i>Cats or dogs?</i>

14:55.311 --> 14:57.813
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Um... cats?</i>

14:57.896 --> 14:59.648
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Oh, I'm so glad you said that.</i>

14:59.732 --> 15:01.650
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>(laughs) Okay, okay.</i>

15:01.734 --> 15:03.152
<i>-Coffee or tea?</i>
<i>-Uh, coffee.</i>

15:03.235 --> 15:05.321
<i>But only Americanos</i>
<i>with one shot</i>

15:05.404 --> 15:07.156
<i>and preferably from the...</i>

15:07.239 --> 15:08.824
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>I'm convinced that being</i>

15:08.907 --> 15:10.492
<i>an only child has</i>
<i>made me an introvert.</i>

15:10.576 --> 15:11.785
{\an5}<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>I have always said</i>
<i>the same thing.</i>

