<i>-Yeah.</i>

15:13.412 --> 15:14.330
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>And on Christmas morning,</i>

15:14.413 --> 15:15.998
<i>my grandma used to make</i>
<i>these eggnog pancakes.</i>

15:16.081 --> 15:17.833
<i>And I swear they would get</i>

15:17.916 --> 15:20.169
<i>-the whole family drunk.</i>
<i>-I always wanted to hike</i>

15:20.252 --> 15:23.464
<i>the Appalachian Trail, but I do</i>
<i>worry that I'd get dehydrated</i>

15:23.547 --> 15:25.799
{\an5}<i>-and definitely break a toe.</i>
<i>-I think I'd worry</i>
<i>more about bears.</i>

15:25.883 --> 15:27.676
<i>I grew up in this town</i>
<i>where you could hear the bells</i>

15:27.760 --> 15:29.386
<i>from this church down</i>
<i>the street, St. Joseph's...</i>

15:29.470 --> 15:31.513
<i>I run into the first room</i>
<i>I can see,</i>

15:31.597 --> 15:33.682
{\an5}<i>-and thank God it's</i>
<i>actually a bathroom.</i>
<i>-No, stop it.</i>

15:33.766 --> 15:36.393
{\an5}<i>-This is too embarrassing,</i>
<i>come on.</i>
<i>-So... so I pull my pants down.</i>

15:36.477 --> 15:38.520
<i>-Yeah?</i>
<i>-And as soon as that happens...</i>

15:38.604 --> 15:40.022
<i>I want you to watch,</i>

15:40.105 --> 15:41.190
<i>watch how he puts the cue</i>
<i>behind his back.</i>

15:41.273 --> 15:42.691
-Oh, yes!
<i>-I told you</i>

15:42.775 --> 15:44.526
<i>-you were gonna like this game!</i>
-Ball potted!

15:44.610 --> 15:47.529
<i>Oh, this is the best game in...</i>

15:47.613 --> 15:49.323
<i>One thing</i>
<i>I have always wondered:</i>

15:49.406 --> 15:51.325
<i>what it would be like</i>
<i>to live on one of these</i>

15:51.408 --> 15:53.994
{\an5}<i>-cargo ships.</i>
<i>-You know, I'm guessing</i>
<i>smelly, cold,</i>

15:54.078 --> 15:56.038
<i>wet, bad food?</i>

15:56.121 --> 15:57.581
<i>Want me to keep going?</i>

15:57.665 --> 15:58.832
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Okay, all right,</i>

15:58.916 --> 16:00.918
<i>so I am thinking that...</i>

16:01.001 --> 16:02.920
{\an5}<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Ooh, I'm thinking</i>
<i>a scoop of mint chip?</i>

16:03.003 --> 16:05.798
-Can I get one...
