16:05.881 --> 16:08.342
Excuse me, can I get two scoops
of mint chip, please, sir?

16:09.802 --> 16:10.719
Thank you very much.

16:10.803 --> 16:12.012
<i>You win.</i>

16:12.096 --> 16:13.347
<i>You happy?</i>

16:13.430 --> 16:15.724
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Yes!</i>

16:15.808 --> 16:18.185
Thank you so much.

16:23.148 --> 16:24.692
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Oh, my God!</i>

16:24.775 --> 16:26.402
<i>Reginald was a Dimidian?</i>

16:26.485 --> 16:29.405
<i>That was the best</i>
<i>season premiere ever.</i>

16:29.488 --> 16:31.031
{\an5}<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Well, actually,</i>
<i>that was part two</i>

16:31.115 --> 16:33.075
<i>of the</i> Kalokagathia-One
<i>miniseries.</i>

16:33.158 --> 16:34.910
<i>So technically</i>
<i>not the season premiere.</i>

16:34.993 --> 16:36.745
<i>But, in any case,</i>
<i>that's so much better</i>

16:36.829 --> 16:38.205
<i>than the trash they're</i>
<i>making these days, right?</i>

16:38.288 --> 16:39.581
Oh.

16:39.665 --> 16:41.041
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>No wonder it's your favorite.</i>

16:41.125 --> 16:42.751
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Yeah, and we can</i>

16:42.835 --> 16:46.338
<i>watch all four seasons</i>
<i>and the movie together.</i>

16:46.422 --> 16:49.258
<i>(Annie laughs)</i>

16:49.341 --> 16:51.093
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Hey... hey, I have an idea.</i>

16:51.176 --> 16:54.596
<i>Um, let's... talk.</i>

16:54.680 --> 16:55.848
<i>Like, like, talk.</i>

16:55.931 --> 16:57.474
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>But we are talking.</i>

16:57.558 --> 16:59.226
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>But, yeah, but I want</i>

16:59.309 --> 17:01.603
<i>to be closer to you.</i>

17:01.687 --> 17:03.439
<i>Maybe... I don't know.</i>

17:03.522 --> 17:06.275
<i>But maybe we can</i>
<i>meet in person.</i>

17:06.358 --> 17:08.819
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>I, um... (clears throat)</i>

17:08.902 --> 17:10.279
<i>It's complicated.</i>

17:10.362 --> 17:12.614
<i>-Look, I'm tired.</i>
<i>-What...?</i>

17:12.698 --> 17:14.324
<i>I'll talk to you tomorrow,</i>
<i>okay? Good night, Phil.</i>

17:14.407 --> 17:15.951
{\an5}<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Whoa, hold on,</i>
<i>wait, wait, wait.</i>

17:16.034 --> 17:17.118
<i>Annie?</i>

17:19.704 --> 17:22.124
<i>Okay.</i>

17:43.228 --> 17:44.813
(mumbles)

17:44.897 --> 17:46.690
(chuckling):
Come on.

17:54.072 --> 17:56.784
<i>What the hell?</i>

17:56.867 --> 17:58.535
<i>Annie, you're married?</i>

17:58.619 --> 18:00.329
{\an5}<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>We never said</i>
<i>we were exclusive.</i>

18:00.412 --> 18:02.372
<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Oh, my God.</i>

18:02.456 --> 18:05.292
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Sorry, that was a... bad joke.</i>

18:05.375 --> 18:07.628
<i>-I'm sorry, but...</i>
