18:07.711 --> 18:09.838
<i>it's-it's-it's, that's such</i>
<i>a huge detail to leave out.</i>

18:09.922 --> 18:11.882
{\an5}<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>I guess you looked me up</i>
<i>after all, huh?</i>

18:11.965 --> 18:14.176
{\an5}<i>PHIL:</i>
<i>Well, yeah... (stammers)</i>
<i>I'm glad I did now,</i>

18:14.259 --> 18:16.845
<i>'cause when were you</i>
<i>planning on telling me this?</i>

18:16.929 --> 18:18.222
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Yes.</i>

18:18.305 --> 18:20.849
<i>I am married.</i>

18:20.933 --> 18:22.810
<i>But I haven't been</i>
<i>happy for years.</i>

18:22.893 --> 18:25.395
<i>And to be honest,</i>
<i>I feel trapped.</i>

18:25.479 --> 18:28.524
<i>Let's just say...</i>

18:28.607 --> 18:31.860
<i>he's not a great guy.</i>

18:31.944 --> 18:34.029
<i>And then you come along.</i>

18:34.112 --> 18:37.032
<i>It just feels so good</i>
<i>to be listened to again.</i>

18:37.115 --> 18:39.910
<i>I've... I've never met someone</i>

18:39.993 --> 18:43.330
<i>who gets me like you do, Phil.</i>

18:43.413 --> 18:46.041
Me neither.

18:50.087 --> 18:52.881
-(clattering outside)
-(gasps)

18:54.258 --> 18:56.635
(truck rumbling outside)

19:02.307 --> 19:05.185
<i>Annie?</i>

19:05.269 --> 19:06.687
<i>You awake?</i>

19:08.438 --> 19:10.899
Annie?

19:10.983 --> 19:12.442
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>Hi.</i>

19:12.526 --> 19:15.070
<i>Are you okay?</i>

19:15.153 --> 19:17.030
Wow.

19:17.114 --> 19:18.824
Wow, I didn't know
if you could hear me

19:18.907 --> 19:20.200
if I was talking out loud.

19:20.284 --> 19:22.119
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>That's crazy.</i>

19:22.202 --> 19:24.371
<i>I guess I can hear you as long</i>
<i>as you're thinking of me,</i>

19:24.454 --> 19:26.456
<i>one way or another.</i>

19:27.875 --> 19:30.127
I wish you were here.

19:30.210 --> 19:32.629
<i>ANNIE:</i>
<i>I'm here.</i>

19:37.342 --> 19:39.761
Hey, you wonder...?

19:39.845 --> 19:42.097
You ever wonder why...

19:42.180 --> 19:44.308
you're here?

19:44.391 --> 19:47.144
Bees pollinate flowers and...

19:48.854 --> 19:51.773
...worms decompose
dead things and...

19:53.358 --> 19:54.776
